ABOUT IMMACULATE CONCEPTION PARISH

MISSION STATEMENT

We, the people of Immaculate Conception Parish in Ewa, declare

our firm loyalty to our Lord Jesus Christ, our Roman Catholic Church, and to the Diocesan Bishop of Honolulu. Our strength is in our unity as a Christian Family of Faith, and we inspire to reach out to everyone with the embrace of Christ.

OFFICE INFORMATION

Immaculate Conception Catholic Church is located on the island of Oahu

and serving the needs of the Ewa communities. Our welcoming parish

prays, ministers and celebrates with one another.

We are located at 91-1298 Renton Road, Ewa, Hawaii 96706. Our office

hours are Monday to Friday from 8:30 am - 4:30 pm. The office is closed

for lunch from 12:30 pm - 1:00 pm. If we can be of assistance, you can

reach us at (808) 681-3701.
